%%{init: {'theme':'neutral'}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start([Register camera node]) --> Deploy[Deploy firmware via SSH+SCP]
    Deploy --> Intrinsic{1 — Intrinsic calibration}
    Intrinsic -->|Checkerboard path| CBCap[Capture 15-30 checkerboard frames<br/>POST /calibrate/intrinsic/capture<br/>~500ms/frame]
    Intrinsic -->|ArUco path| ArCap[Capture 5-10 ArUco snapshots<br/>POST /api/cameras/fid/aruco/capture]
    CBCap --> CBCompute[POST /calibrate/intrinsic/compute<br/>cv2.calibrateCamera<br/>~2s for 3 frames]
    ArCap --> ArCompute[POST /api/cameras/fid/aruco/compute<br/>~a few seconds]
    CBCompute --> Saved[Save to camera:<br/>/opt/slyled/calib/intrinsic_camN.json]
    ArCompute --> Saved
    Intrinsic -.->|skip| FOV[Fall back to FOV-derived K<br/>intrinsic_source = fov-estimate]

    Saved --> Survey[2 — ArUco marker survey]
    FOV --> Survey
    Survey --> MarkerReg[POST /api/aruco/markers<br/>id, size, x/y/z, rx/ry/rz, label]
    MarkerReg --> Coverage[GET /api/aruco/markers/coverage<br/>per-camera visible IDs]
    Coverage --> Enough{>= 3 markers<br/>visible per camera?}
    Enough -->|no| AddMarker[Add marker at<br/>recommendation pin]
    AddMarker --> Coverage
    Enough -->|yes| DarkRef[3 — Dark-reference capture<br/>#651<br/>POST /dark-reference<br/>~100ms/cam]

    DarkRef --> StageMap[4 — Extrinsic solve<br/>POST /api/cameras/fid/stage-map<br/>~5-10s multi-snapshot]
    StageMap --> PnP[Multi-snapshot aggregation<br/>best-per-ID corners<br/>cv2.solvePnP SQPNP -> ITERATIVE]
    PnP --> StoreExt[Store camera.rotation rx/ry/rz<br/>+ position x/y/z<br/>rotationSchemaVersion: 2]

    StoreExt --> Scan[5 — Optional: space scan]
    Scan --> PointCloud[POST /point-cloud per cam<br/>~6.5s/cam metric]
    PointCloud --> Anchor[Depth anchor fit #581<br/>scale + offset]
    Anchor --> Merge[space_mapper SpaceScan<br/>cross-cam filter #582<br/>floor normalize]
    Merge --> Surfaces[surface_analyzer RANSAC<br/>floor + walls + obstacles]
    Surfaces --> Done([Stage geometry ready])

    Scan -.->|skip| Done

    StageMap -.->|RMS > 5px or<br/>too few markers| Error[Calibration error]
    PnP -.->|no convergence| Error
    Error --> Retry[Operator: add markers<br/>or increase snapshots]
    Retry --> Coverage
